  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Investigation of whether injection of the pectoralis muscle with 100 units botulinum toxin
      during breast reconstruction with tissue expanders results in decreased pain using a blinded,
      randomized, controlled trial.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
